data.description:
Energy efficient home by growth homes. Built in 2015 and features an elegant modern look with tile
flooring throughout the first floor, , brand new laminate in stairs and primary bedroom, custom cabinets
and quarts countertops, stainless steel appliances. Upgraded/ remodeled bathrooms, and a beautiful
backyard with turf landscaping to entertain in. 3 bedrooms 2.5 bath with a formal dining area, a huge loft
that can be converted into a 4th bedroom. This gem is located in a a cul-de-sac inside gated community
with a community pool. walking distance to Duck Creek Park. Home has energy efficient windows and
insolation. Must see!
